<A HREF=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=79455 target=new>Player Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=branaman>Branaman</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_purplespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/2/01 2:20:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=177.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to Quad at 45+  ???</span><hr size=1> Specters in oasis.<br>
<br>
Loot is about 1pp avarage in cash<br>
Items are scythes (14pp) bronze scythes (3pp) rusty (newby)<br>
Some mid end jewels like black pearls, peridots<br>
pages/runes/words<br>
<br>
Pull with flux staff<br>
get 4 this way<br>
use levitate to group the over the water<br>
learn distance. In flux range but outside their cast range.<br>
<br>
learn to group them by their casting. A casting specter does not move, and therefore the rest of the group can get closer. Their drains hit for around 40 hp dmg.<br>
<br>
But rounded up in water, then pulled towards orc camp on wall side. snared there, then quadded with CoF along beach towards ocean. will drop them around the inn there. If people start to pull from your quad, continue with what you have. (3) if less, or they messed up your quad and continue to do so after warning. Pull towards them, then gate out. Let them handle all 4.<br>
<br>
With C2, or with mana items and C1, you can keep up with the whole Island (4 corners) and the Tower (1 inside 3 on top)<br>
