<br>
With 200 int and 405+ mana  I could complete a quad at 46 (any combo of lightfoots, watchers or provens) and still have harvest left over.<br>
<br>
I'm not sure if you could do it without some additional +mana items but you could easily double kite them or pull singles and root nuke.<br>
<br>
From what I have heard the provens are higher level but the watchers seem to resist me more than the other two.<br>
<br>
I have gone from 46 to 50 in about a week killing these and it only gets easier as you level.<br>
<br>
Haven't seen a green one yet at 50 but I hear that at 51 some of them start to green out, but at 51 its off to CS anyway.<br>
<br>
Give it a try I think you will like it.<br>
